Enum CalcStepRecord.StepType

    CalcStepRecord
    public static enum CalcStepRecord.StepType
extends Enum<CalcStepRecord.StepType>
    Calculation step type. 1. If an expression string refers (at some point) to a dependent argument then calculation step handling this dependent argument calculation will be marked as type Argument. 2. If an expression string refers (at some point) to a user function then calculation step handling this function calculation will be marked as type Function. 3. if a calculation step handles just a part related to a typical expression then this step will be marked as type Expression.
